    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Jackets made with a box pleat on either side of the center front and a box pleat at center back, also having pockets on the hips and a self belt.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
